{"tid":1664441,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【共慘黨當你港豬有牙吖？】 智利爆發地鐵示威僅兩日，總統宣佈撤回加價，指民主是虛心聆聽","createTime":"2019-10-20T06:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T06:15:48.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7a95df301306d3855d3135517af9d59eebbfd4","tid":1664441,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"智利總統回應抗議地鐵加價的示威者訴求，宣佈撤回加價決定，並會制定新法例檢討車資。<br />\n<br />\n在首都聖地亞哥街頭，軍方施放水炮及催淚彈驅散示威者，示威者拒絕撤離，繼續跟士兵對峙，又焚燒雜物築起防線。多架巴士被燒成廢鐵，最少70個地鐵站受破壞。營運公司估計損失達二千萬美元，暫時未知鐵路服務能否在週一恢復。<br />\n<br />\n智利早前先加電費一成，之後再將繁忙時段地鐵車資調高近百分之四，觸發週五民眾激烈示威，令聖地亞哥進入緊急狀態。<br />\n<br />\n當地有蒙面示威者縱火及破壞地鐵站，一度全線136個站關閉，有士兵巡邏聖地亞哥街頭，並宣佈晚上10時至早上7時宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n起初批評示威者搞破壞的總統皮涅拉作出讓步，宣佈撤回地鐵加價，指民主是由虛心聆聽民眾訴求來建立，亦會制定特別法例，檢討地鐵車資。 <br />\n<br />\n戰鬥民族智利仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRfKNKMndQGUBlDMGWAzq0YiaP1dIH8seT6iL5_RqohSBBnrkt3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRfKNKMndQGUBlDMGWAzq0YiaP1dIH8seT6iL5_RqohSBBnrkt3&h=49c24405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQZrbsQJRCVAWRJb0-f6IF2JiW22nSjzpimZXF3GsmvYQPlx-EP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQZrbsQJRCVAWRJb0-f6IF2JiW22nSjzpimZXF3GsmvYQPlx-EP&h=aa2ba39e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSOy2ip1zkWiPafjYHl7mrxW5PVBR0n8Bv7t_131YvDApf1p-WV\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSOy2ip1zkWiPafjYHl7mrxW5PVBR0n8Bv7t_131YvDApf1p-WV&h=6f8da534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191019/_2019101921535210547.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191019%2F_2019101921535210547.jpg&h=29ff051e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}